{"type": "article", "id": 26645, "title": "表现地震的花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702105759edswqW8IKPTUY4Jc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">从大自然中汲取设计灵感并不是件新鲜事，将灾难通过美学呈现就不多见了。设计师 Jonathan Radetz 根据地震仪记录下的图像，制作了被命名为 Italy 和 New Zealand 的两款<a href=\"http://dua-collection.com/en/collection/seismographic-vases\">花瓶</a>。他的这个创意在不久前还赢得了 2016 年德国设计奖，<a href=\"http://www.dua-shop.de/en/shop/home-accessories/new-zealand-seismographic-vases/\">售价为 178 欧元</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105757JrcaB5HwVMWLz623.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021057574eyP5mA8K3ZTM6H2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105758DrOPkuEgVqThLpMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105758Zrz8RkYyAqxdI1Wu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}